title: An Old Spanish Custom (1935) BUSTER KEATON

sources.title: An Old Spanish Custom (1935) BUSTER KEATON
sources.description:
Stars: Buster Keaton, Lupita Tovar, Lyn Harding
Director: Adrian Brunel

A bumbling yachtsman sails to the South of Spain and trips on a fiery seductress, only to become the pawn in her dangerous game of love.
